Linux :
~~~~~~~
make -f Makefile.cvs
./configure --prefix=<your_dir>
make
make install

<your_dir>/bin contains executable
<your_dir>/lib contains plugins

Command Line :
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
options are
-p | --port <port_number>
-l | --load <path_to_plugin>
-c | --connect <path_to_connection_plugin>

Sigma